BASE STATS

STR . strength
INT . intelligence

REF . reflex
CBT . combat

CON . constitution
KNO . knowledge

------------------------------------------------------------

COMBAT STATS

ATK . attack = STR and CBT
DEF . defense = STR and REF
ATKSPD . attack speed = STR and CON

MATK . magical attack = INT and CBT
MDEF . magical defense = INT and REF
MATKSPD . magical attack speed = INT and KNO

HP . health points = CON
FLOW . flow = KNO
